<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.6.8">
<l>neṟittiṭ ṭameṉkū ḻainaṉṉē riḻaiyō ṭuṭaṉā yavilleṉ ṉavallē yataṉai</l>
<l>yiṟuttiṭ ṭavaḷiṉ pamaṉpō ṭaṇaintiṭ ṭiḷaṅkoṟ ṟavaṉāyt tuḷaṅkā tamunnīr</l>
<l>ceṟittiṭ ṭilaṅkai malaṅka varakkaṉ ceḻunīṇ muṭitō ḷoṭutāḷ tuṇiya</l>
<l>vaṟuttiṭ ṭavaṉkāṇ miṉiṉṟāyc ciyarā laḷaiveṇṇe yuṇṭāp puṇṭirun tavaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having snapped apart that which was suited to strength</l>
<l rend="indent">called the bow that belongs with the one</l>
<l rend="indent">of curled, soft hair and well-strung jewels,</l>
<l>Embracing her with love and delight as the young king,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who, having blocked up the immobilized sea,</l>
<l>Cut up the demon so that Laṅkā was ruined,</l>
<l rend="indent">severing his splendid high crowns, arms, and legs,</l>
<l>See, he is the one who was bound, having eaten the butter</l>
<l rend="indent">churned by the herder women today.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
